org.batfish.common

Class Version

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.common.Version

  • public final class Version
extends java.lang.Object
    A utility class to determine the version of Batfish being used and check compatibility between different endpoints across API calls.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static java.lang.String INCOMPATIBLE_VERSION
      A special version string that is incompatible with all other version.
